client: ssh from
server: ssh to

on client 
ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C "text"
leave location and password blank


on server
sudo adduser student
sudo passwd -l student

on client
ssh-copy-id student@clientip

or cat the key and manually put it in/home/student/.ssh/authorized_keys on server

on server
sudo nano /etc/ssh/sshd_config
PubkeyAuthentication yes

restart ssh on server
